{"id":402449,"date":[{"year":1960,"month":2,"day":18}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"157","ytitle":"","mtitle":"扬水站电磨","ftitle":"","authors":["郭煌"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭煌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水卷起了漩涡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电力推动着石磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨锥螺陀似的旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出水车般的鸣叫:咯，咯……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面粉沿齿缝流出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细得好象乳酪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女拿小帚轻扫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心和磨一起唱歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前农人挨饿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少磨生锈呀，门上了锁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社化以前石磨忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但磨得太慢，不出活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今电力把磨叶冲击，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一小时能磨几十箩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬水站呀是幸福站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你听，时代在电机里高歌!"}]}